sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: Outbound Network Connection Initiated By Script Interpreter
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects a script interpreter wscript/cscript opening a network connection to a non-local network. Adversaries may use script to download malicious payloads.

attributes.magic: PE32 executable (GUI) Intel 80386, for MS Windows

threat_severity.level_description: Severity HIGH because it was considered trojan. Other contributing factor was that it could not be run in sandboxes.

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert tcp $HOME_NET any -> $EXTERNAL_NET $HTTP_PORTS ( msg:"MALWARE-CNC Win.Trojan.Malear variant outbound connection"; flow:to_server,established; http_uri; content:"/news2/news_dir/index.php",fast_pattern,nocase; http_header; content:!"User-Agent",nocase; metadata:impact_flag red; service:http; reference:url,virustotal.com/en/file/281828d6f5bd377f91c6283c34896d0483b08ac2167d34e981fbea871893c919/analysis/; classtype:trojan-activity; sid:41686; rev:2; )

alert tcp $HOME_NET any -> $EXTERNAL_NET $HTTP_PORTS ( msg:"MALWARE-CNC Win.Trojan.Malear variant outbound connection"; flow:to_server,established; http_raw_uri; bufferlen:<60; http_uri; content:"_put.jpg",fast_pattern,nocase; http_header; content:!"User-Agent",nocase; http_uri; pcre:"/\x2F[0-9A-F]{8,10}_put\.jpg$/im"; metadata:impact_flag red; service:http; reference:url,virustotal.com/en/file/281828d6f5bd377f91c6283c34896d0483b08ac2167d34e981fbea871893c919/analysis/; classtype:trojan-activity; sid:41687; rev:2; )
